  5번 → Flipkart (btn_square_flipkart:https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jCVIkW-ULS5GO9zD-dpDEV0Jsp7dTU4d/view?usp=drive_link)
  6번 → Amazon India (btn_square_amazon_india:https://drive.google.com/file/d/14jXDZSGLbiIehaCUvaK6ytpjW1fEZO7G/view?usp=drive_link)
